    <div class="container">
        <div class="gallery-header">
            <h2><img src="images/gallery.png" alt="Gallery Icon"> Department Gallery</h2>
            <p>Explore highlights from our department, including campus events, student activities, research projects, and facility tours.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="gallery">
            <div class="gallery-item">
                <img src="images/event1.jpg" alt="Department annual seminar with students and faculty gathering in the conference hall">
                <div class="gallery-item-info">
                    <h3>Annual Seminar 2025</h3>
                    <p>Faculty and students gather for our annual tech seminar featuring guest speakers from leading tech companies.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="gallery-item">
                <img src="images/event2.jpg" alt="Students participating in hackathon competition with laptops and coding activities">
                <div class="gallery-item-info">
                    <h3>Hackathon Event</h3>
                    <p>Students showcase their coding skills in our annual hackathon with prizes and recognition for outstanding projects.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="gallery-item">
                <img src="images/event3.jpg" alt="Campus lab facility showing computer workstations and students working on projects">
                <div class="gallery-item-info">
                    <h3>Lab Facilities</h3>
                    <p>State-of-the-art computing labs equipped with modern hardware and software for practical learning and research.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="gallery-item">
                <img src="images/event4.jpg" alt="Student presentation at academic conference with slides and audience">
                <div class="gallery-item-info">
                    <h3>Research Presentations</h3>
                    <p>Students present their research findings at national and international academic conferences and seminars.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="gallery-item">
                <img src="images/event5.jpg" alt="Graduation ceremony with graduates in academic robes and families celebrating achievement">
                <div class="gallery-item-info">
                    <h3>Graduation Ceremony</h3>
                    <p>Celebrating the achievements and success of our graduates as they embark on their professional careers.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="gallery-item">
                <img src="images/event6.jpg" alt="Faculty workshop and collaboration meeting with computers and discussion materials">
                <div class="gallery-item-info">
                    <h3>Faculty Workshop</h3>
                    <p>Regular faculty workshops to update teaching methods, research techniques, and professional development activities.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

